{"tid":1608032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今日港島呢個場面，可以話係已經達成活動本身想要既目標，又未有畀衝突蓋過","createTime":"2019-10-01T06:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T08:57:01.000Z","uid":54684,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3060d7d575629e0c19ed519b25a3e5b74f4f40","tid":1608032,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>路透社直播中</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/Reuters/status/1178922500584927232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1178922500584927232&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=a45dc698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/Reuters/status/1178922500584927232</a>"},{"pid":"219068c3aaf28b1a0fcb1e10862c9a7455cac0dc","tid":1608032,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed721b528a3d36e466ece25b94263e9be393655","tid":1608032,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:01:35.000Z","msg":"nice"},{"pid":"fabf944e06b84a1dccd356f54c22132cbc6bb183","tid":1608032,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b8d1643163ef2b6cc70c5c9a7c3f1f2238f2e7","tid":1608032,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9b469339f54e5da5b46564ff88696608862e9e","tid":1608032,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:03:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">昨日警察不斷恐嚇大家十一唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，十一當日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e56adb8e2fb1f87455666b85abaa17b03d49e60","tid":1608032,"uid":289565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"吳克儉局長支持港獨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係我地既大台 教育局長帶領香港人抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1607985/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1607985/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/profile.php?v=info&amp;lst=750740283%3A100010324240751%3A1569912393&amp;id=100010324240751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fv%3Dinfo%26l